name: Mreq-DeliveryStatus Report
query: Select pi.material_request, mr.modified_by, mr.status, mr.docstatus, pi.parent, pi.item_code, pi.description, pi.expected_delivery_date, pi.revised_delivery_date, pi.qty, pi.received_qty, (pi.received_qty/pi.qty*100) from `tabPurchase Order Item` pi, `tabMaterial Request` mr where pi.material_request = mr.name and mr.docstatus in ("0", "1") ;
